<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8389697>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. (A) LectotypeF0055223(https://fm-digital-assets.fieldmuseum.org/55/970/V0055223F.jpg) designatedfor the name Agarista pistrix G.Don (heterotypic synonym of the accepted name Agarista subrotunda (Pohl) G.Don) based on the original material available. (B) Epitype specimen A.F.M. Glaziou 17110 (P04507711) (http://coldb.mnhn.fr/catalognumber/mnhn/p/p04507711), designated as an interpretative type to complement the lectotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8389697/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

